# China's Woes During the 1500

## Causes
Intensive farming caused depletion of land, but pop. is growing. This results in Malthusian Sadness!

* The [[KBhHIST201LittleIceAge]] The Little Ice Age
* North American crops caused overpopulation
* Internal governmental decline [[KBhHIST201ChinasDecline1500]] China's Decline in the 1500s

## The Woes
Widespread famine because of the bad produce of China's farmland. 

